article.description: — Vonterius Woolbright scored 19 points as Western Carolina beat North Alabama 81-63 on Sunday night.
article.headline: Woolbright scores 19 as Western Carolina downs North Alabama 81-63
article.linkText: Woolbright scores 19 as Western Carolina downs North Alabama 81-63
article.story: CULLOWHEE, N.C. -- — Vonterius Woolbright scored 19 points as Western Carolina beat North Alabama 81-63 on Sunday night. Woolbright had 15 rebounds and six assists for the Catamounts (5-0). Tre Jackson scored 18 points while going 6 of 12 (4 for 8 from 3-point range), and added seven rebounds. Kamar Robertson had 16 points and was 7 of 8 shooting (2 for 3 from 3-point range). The Lions (3-3) were led in scoring by Damien Forrest, who finished with 13 points. North Alabama also got 11 points from Jacari Lane. KJ Johnson also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
